# Data. The Phase 1 MVP's 5 official card PDFs (~4.6MB total, source_url recorded in
# database/seed.py) are committed so a clean clone + CI can reproduce the seeded DB and the
# golden-set evaluation gates (Section 18.4) without depending on live issuer URLs at build
# time. Section 7.4's "keep raw PDFs out of the repo" guidance is the right call at a larger
# scale (many issuers, large files) - revisit with Git LFS or object storage if the corpus
# grows past a handful of small documents.
data/processed_chunks/

